149","tid":403291,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:22:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有丁權你都要識村啲人先攞到地㗎<br />\n<br />\n利申 有丁權但係唔識人</blockquote><br />\n唔等政府批地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6673f55fc44d6d24d2a4c77536d4c2904d882bca","tid":403291,"uid":51294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:29:42.000Z","msg":"大陸深圳幾千呎起十層八層先係贏家"},{"pid":"c0348c6182e03fd0032de1e1ecb9a57390ff9bea","tid":403291,"uid":126831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:45:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一出世有得起三層獨立屋<br />\n人生贏家</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger<br />\n利申：有丁有地有丁屋"},{"pid":"bd5e98e4c9037f79821b2c641b632775697ce37e","tid":403291,"uid":121676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T15:48:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一出世有得起三層獨立屋<br />\n人生贏家</blockquote><br />\n冇丁權<br />\n但有你所講既野"},{"pid":"e4025da9ee0b45fbfb30c2395ec179ae093d27c7","tid":403291,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T16:11:44.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦大哥,一定要齊哂丁權，土地同埋建築費先起到三層高小型屋宇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有d圍頭仔係有丁無地，有d就直頭無錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近十幾廿年來吸引咗一班有圍村背景既牛屎佬成立乜乜鳩鳩發展/土地顧問公司收購佢地丁權再大搞懷似套丁/飛丁項目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 元朗至流浮山一帶就大概10-20萬一個丁權，如果係西貢大網仔路一帶/近海景既話，隨時可以賣到80-90萬一個丁權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁項目竣工之後，呢d三層高小型屋宇就可以賣到1300-1700萬島（元朗區），如果係西貢區分分鐘要1800-2000萬樓上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318d7a1863a432f776499cda89b63da1eb04e700","tid":403291,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T16:17:13.000Z","msg":"又一個唔知咩係丁權嘅人衝出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}